<item>
            <title>[HBASE-3707] Flush memstore after a configurable number of inserts not simply based on size</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3707</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Memstore upsert performance may be impacted by having a large number of values in the map. Consider flushing the store after a configurable number of inserts.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12502631">HBASE-3707</key>
            <summary>Flush memstore after a configurable number of inserts not simply based on size</summary>
